capita GHG emissions were 1.7 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 2.14 GtCO2, or about 0% of global
emissions to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
